# Day 5 - Gray to Binary Converter

## ðŸ“˜ Description
This module converts a **Gray code** input to its **Binary equivalent** using bitwise logic.

## ðŸ”§ Tools & Language
- Verilog HDL
- Simulated using ModelSim

## ðŸ§® Logic
B[n-1] = G[n-1]
B[i] = B[i+1] ^ G[i] (for i from n-2 to 0)

